## 4. Setup Supabase Project

Langkah-langkah:

1. Login supabase.com -> “New Project”
1. Nama: apick-prod (atau apick-dev untuk development)
1. Region: Southeast Asia (Singapore)
1. Generate password -> SIMPAN di password manager
1. Setelah project ready, catat:
- Project URL: https://xxxxx.supabase.co
- anon key: eyJxxx…
- service_role key: eyJxxx… (JANGAN share ini)
1. Di Supabase dashboard -> Authentication -> Providers:
- Enable Google (masukkan OAuth Client ID dari Google Cloud Console)
- Enable Phone (free tier cukup untuk dev, nanti pakai Twilio/MessageBird untuk prod)
1. Di Supabase dashboard -> Database -> SQL Editor:
- Nanti kamu akan paste migration SQL dari dokumen product concept di sini

## 5. Setup Gemini API

1. Buka aistudio.google.com
1. Login dengan Google account
1. “Get API Key” -> “Create API Key”
1. Simpan API key
1. Test di terminal:

```bash
curl "https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/gemini-2.5-flash:generateContent?key=YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"contents":[{"parts":[{"text":"Say hello in Indonesian"}]}]}'
```

1. Kalau response muncul = API key works

