# TROUBLESHOOTING COMMON ISSUES

-----

## “App gak mau start / crash”

```
1. Terminal: npx expo start --clear
2. Kalau masih error: rm -rf node_modules && npm install
3. Kalau masih: rm -rf .expo && npx expo start --clear
4. Share error message ke Claude, pakai HOTFIX PROMPT
```

## “Supabase gak connect”

```
1. Cek .env file: EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL dan EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY ada dan benar
2. Cek Supabase dashboard: project masih running? (free tier pause setelah 7 hari inactive)
3. Kalau paused: klik "Restore" di Supabase dashboard
4. Test connection: buka Supabase dashboard -> SQL Editor -> run "SELECT 1" 
```

## “Claude bikin error baru saat fix error lama”

```
1. STOP. Jangan biarkan Claude lanjut.
2. Copy-paste ERROR SPIRAL PROMPT (Section C2)
3. Biasanya root cause-nya: type/interface yang diubah tanpa update semua file yang pakai
4. Kalau parah: git stash (revert ke last working state), mulai ulang task dari scratch
```

## “Claude mulai lupa / repeat / inconsistent”

```
1. Context window hampir penuh
2. Jalankan CONTEXT LIMIT APPROACHING prompt (Section C4)
3. Tutup session, buka terminal baru
4. Jalankan Claude Code lagi
5. Mulai dengan RECOVERY PROMPT (Section A2)
```

## “Web portal gak bisa diakses”

```
1. Cek Vercel dashboard: deployment successful?
2. Cek domain: DNS pointing ke Vercel?
3. Kalau pakai custom domain (apick.id): DNS propagation bisa 24-48 jam
4. Sementara pakai Vercel default URL: apick-portal.vercel.app/xx/xx
```

## “Push notification gak masuk”

```
1. Expo push notification butuh physical device (gak jalan di emulator)
2. Cek: Expo push token tersimpan di database? (Supabase dashboard -> profiles table)
3. Cek: notifikasi di-allow di settings HP?
4. Test: buka https://expo.dev/notifications -> kirim test notification ke token
```

