# GIT WORKFLOW

-----

## Branch Strategy (Simple)

```
main          -> production code, selalu working
dev           -> development, merge ke main saat phase selesai
```

Gak perlu feature branches untuk solo developer. Keep it simple.

## Commit Pattern

```bash
# Setiap selesai 1-3 tasks:
git add .
git commit -m "Phase 0: task 0.1-0.3 - init project, dependencies, NativeWind"

# Setiap selesai 1 phase:
git add .
git commit -m "Phase 1 complete: Module Warga MVP"
git push

# Setiap quality gate pass:
git tag -a v0.1.0 -m "Quality Gate 1 passed - Warga MVP"
git push --tags
```

## Version Tags

|Tag   |Milestone                                    |
|------|---------------------------------------------|
|v0.0.1|Phase 0 complete (foundation)                |
|v0.1.0|Phase 1 complete (Warga MVP)                 |
|v0.2.0|Phase 2 complete (+Lapak Pedagang)           |
|v0.3.0|Phase 3 complete (+Sewa Properti)            |
|v0.4.0|Phase 4 complete (+Lapak Advanced)           |
|v0.5.0|Phase 5 complete (+Hajat)                    |
|v1.0.0|Phase 6 complete (Full app, ready for launch)|

